      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为工业物联网场景画一个状态图，核心是从PLC逻辑单元开始，经过边缘节点，最终把遥测数据发出去。起点是IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic，它需要先进入Connecting状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_PLC_Logic",
        "Connecting"
