      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Connecting是中间状态。那Connecting之后应该有两个去向吧？一个是连到边缘节点，另一个是进入已连接状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connecting",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "Connected"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Connecting既要指向IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode表示物理连接建立，也要流转到Connected表示逻辑就绪。之后进入Idle空闲态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Connecting",
        "IoT_Industrial_EdgeNode",
        "Connected",
        "Idle"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，Idle画好了。从Idle出发，我看到有发送数据的需求，还有超时处理，另外应该有个关闭连接的出口？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "Closed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。Idle可以进入Sending发数据，发完回到Idle；也可能遇到Timeout超时，这时候要通知执行器控制器IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController。另外Idle也能直接Closed关闭。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Idle",
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "IoT_Industrial_ActuatorController",
        "Closed"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Sending和Timeout之间有关联吗？比如发送过程中也可能超时？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sending",
        "Timeout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Sending也要能转到Timeout。最后Closed状态要输出到IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream，表示遥测流结束。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Sending",
        "Timeout",
        "Closed",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
